BT 1 0 0 1 0 74 Tm /F1 10 Tf 12 TL 2.043775 Tw (One of the most important aspects of teaching is preparation. This implies a couple of things. First, the) Tj T* 0 Tw .665232 Tw (instructor must know the subject very well; it is very difficult to teach with authority when the students detect) Tj T* 0 Tw .472136 Tw (gaps in your knowledge. Sometimes this requires reviewing or learning new material, which was the case for) Tj T* 0 Tw .900834 Tw (me when I was a teaching assistant for Computer Architecture and Logic Design. Although I am a primarily) Tj T* 0 Tw .321859 Tw (software-oriented computer scientist, I approached these hardware courses as an opportunity to reinforce my) Tj T* 0 Tw .295261 Tw (previous education and was able to contribute new lab software and tutorials. From this experience, I learned) Tj T* 0 Tw (that teaching is not only an opportunity to share your knowledge, but to grow and expand it as well.) Tj T* ET
